<h2>News for the Foresight Community</h2>
<ul>
<li>Warnings: Worst-Case Scenarios</li>
<li>Hot Topic: Arab Futures</li>
<li>Publication: <i>The Suicide of the Jews</i></li>
<li>Leaders Lend an Ear: Thomas Frey, Jeremy Rifkin</li>
<li>Foresight Report: Technology Work 2030</li>
<li>Appointment: New Editor for <i>World Future Review</i></li>
